#: ../../../source/Releases/Release-Kilted-Kaiju.rst:183
msgid ""
"Included two new packages which provide an extensible mechanism for creating "
"a test fixture for RMW-based communication isolation. It is modeled closely "
"after the rmw and rmw_implementation API."
